<h2>Engineering Science Education Conference!</h2>
<p>
	The Division of Engineering Science at the University of Toronto is pleased to invite you to the 10th Annual Engineering Science Education Conference (ESEC)!
</p>
<p>
	ESEC is an annual conference bringing distinguished speakers from across the globe to Engsci students. Attend the talks to get inspired with different career possibilities and network with renowned representatives from industry and academia. All EngScis are encouraged to attend!</p>
<p>
	Here are the details:
	<ul>
		<li><b>Date:</b> Jan 23rd, 2015</li>
		<li><b>Time:</b> All Day</li>
		<li><b>Location:</b> BA 1130 and BA 1160</li>
	</ul>
</p>
 
<p>
Want to find out more about our amazing speakers and register?

Visit our <a href="https://my.engsci.utoronto.ca/esec/"> website</a>.
</p>

